messages:
Name: Jonas Svensson
Nationality: Norway
Date of Birth: March 6, 1993
Position: Defender
Current club: AZ
Eredivisie clubs played for: AZ

Jonas Svensson, the AZ defender, has appeared in a strong number of their Eredivisie games in 2020/2021, making 18 appearances overall and accumulating 1,414 minutes of playing time. He has started in 17 of these appearances across their 34 fixtures and been used as a substitute on one occasion.

Svensson last played in a league match on May 16 for AZ against Heracles. He provided an assist in that game for his side in the team's 5-0 success. This season he has registered three league assists. He has amassed three yellow cards, as well as sent off once.
In last season's Eredivisie, Svensson appeared in 23 games for AZ, scored one goal and provided five assists.
Svensson joined AZ in January 2017 from Rosenborg, for whom he made 157 league appearances in total, scoring 11 goals and providing 13 assists.
